title: Kundan
subTitle: Thakur Shamsher Singh, a wealthy criminal, tries to befriend a newly-appointed police officer in order to gain his favour, only to find out that the policeman is immune to his tactics.

title: Shehzada
subTitle: Bantu, a middle-class man, grows up being neglected by his cold-hearted father, Valmiki. However, his world is shaken when he learns that he was switched at birth.

title: Abhinetri
subTitle: Stage artist Anjana takes a break from her career after marrying the love of her life, Shekhar. As time passes, their individual expectations start to clash and put a strain on their relationship.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Love in Tokyo
subTitle: While in Japan to pick up his orphaned nephew, Ashok becomes locked in a romantic misadventure with Asha, a troubled woman who is a master of disguises.

title: Lav Kush
subTitle: After Ram returns to Ayodhya, Sita is forced to go into exile. She gives birth to twins Lav and Kush, who later go to Ayodhya to attain blessings of Ram and recite the Ramayan.

title: Pyaasa Sawan
subTitle: Chandrakant, a wealthy man, observes his son Ravi neglecting his wife for his career and decides to intervene to save Ravi's marriage.

title: Paappi Devataa
subTitle: Ram and Rahim become best friends after the latter offers shelter to Ram when he comes to Bombay. However, Ram is unaware that Rahim is involved in illegal activities.

title: Kudrat Ka Kanoon
subTitle: When the good doctor Vijay is falsely accused and imprisoned, his wife and daughter, desperately seeking justice, are terrorised and slandered by the harsh eyes of the society.

title: Muqabla
subTitle: Two dreaded gangsters call it a truce and become friends. The peace is broken when both fall in love with the same girl and neither is willing to sacrifice their love.

title: Shagird
subTitle: Professor Brij, who is sworn to bachelorhood, mentors Ramesh, who wants to be just like him. However, when the professor falls for Poonam, he faces a dilemma.

title: Khushboo
subTitle: Kusum and Brindavan get married as children but are separated due to a misunderstanding. Years later, they cross paths again and try to fix their relationship.

title: Himmat
subTitle: Raghu, a reformed criminal, rescues a woman and soon their love blossoms into a happy marriage. However, when the police arrive to catch him in connection with a murder, their lives turn upside down.

title: Azad Desh Ke Ghulam
subTitle: Bharti, a young girl studying law, belongs to a rich family. All hell breaks loose when she discovers the truth about her father's methods of amassing wealth.

title: Anokha Bandhan
subTitle: Anu raises her young brother-in-law like a son after the death of her mother-in-law. But with her own son in the picture, and interference from her mother, the equation begins to change.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja
subTitle: Three friends, orphaned by an evil man, set out to take revenge for their father's murders. They are forced to navigate a complex web of deceit and stolen identities before they can reach their goal.

title: Aap To Aise Na The
subTitle: Vijay, who owns a furniture store, is in love with Varsha. However, Vijay's life takes a drastic turn when she decides to marry his friend Vikram, a rich man, who promises her a better life.

title: Chitchor
subTitle: When Geeta's sister arranges her wedding with a young engineer, their father mistakenly brings the wrong man home. However, as love blossoms between the two, the arrival of a letter startles everyone.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Locket
subTitle: In a majestic kingdom, the treacherous relative of a king plots to seize the throne. However, his path is blocked by the crown prince, whose locket holds the key to a hidden treasure.

title: Aman
subTitle: Dr Gautamdas, a well-educated man from London, moves to Japan during the aftermath of the Hiroshima and Nagasaki bombing, where he falls in love with Meloda.

title: Sanjog
subTitle: A man's parents disapprove of his relationship with a woman and lie to him about her death. However, things take a turn when, years later, his lover becomes his boss at work.

title: Main Aur Mera Haathi
subTitle: Ram swears vengeance against Teja after he is framed and imprisoned for a crime he has not committed. After he is released from jail, Ram befriends an elephant who helps him in his quest.

title: Batwara
subTitle: Amidst the fall of princely states in post-independence India, the friendship between aristocrat Vikram and a peasant is tested. Vikram turns vengeful after his brother is killed in a peasant colony.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.
